Name: Andromeda One
About the game: Andromeda One is an First Person Shooter video game. The game take place in the far future where spatial exploration of galaxy is possible. The hero is in the military and try to bring order in the Andromeda galaxy. The game is an open-world game where the hero has the choice to fight different opponents with different weapons.
